{"tid":40792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[分屍]逸東邨26歲女子墮樓　身體斷開慘死","createTime":"2016-12-15T12:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T05:57:57.000Z","uid":408,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f81b78bdbc8f5b4f1ca3419d70e9e750f57a066f","tid":40792,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:18:39.000Z","msg":"　　事發在下午2時許，一名26歲女子由康逸樓高處墮下，墜落時疑撞及停車場一個金屬上蓋，女子身體斷開多截，墜落地面。救護員接報到場，證實女子已經死亡。警方封鎖現場，正調查案件。<br />\n　　據了解，女事主生前疑受情緒問題困擾。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/15/201835_bf88c648b7b64e0816b1367699ceb6b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F15%2F201835_bf88c648b7b64e0816b1367699ceb6b5.jpg&h=bb76af34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661e42a60dded444c5a36ccec5b21fa4d8ef719d","tid":40792,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfffe97433f5f5f5760c76541a8ddaa35de38034","tid":40792,"uid":8728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0063367b1f03ae7682def5949295d1962530337b","tid":40792,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:20:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma