rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw今日我都聽到佢跳落去前好大聲講左句野<br />\n好似係鬧人既，而且好嬲咁講<br />\n之後過幾秒就聽到呯一聲好大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個下已經feel到啲野，心諗唔係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我望落去個位遮住左睇唔到咩事<br />\n過左陣就聽到警車聲<br />\n<br />\n到5點零6點，有fd sd左條新聞出黎就知咩事了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似係咁諗到佢把聲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nR.i.p <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab50b5ad47f2ab65f8427067dad383fdf7bad4c6","tid":40792,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:03:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14fd9a636d8926e83677960874e06dc8d560551c","tid":40792,"uid":27090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:08:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好大怨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n住果頭既巴打小心D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後都唔敢行嗰到"},{"pid":"715dc5e491fb63c86447e0095d8f087e7a92a96e","tid":40792,"uid":10204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:12:15.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"70d87b3828603a61259b5de2a897ac144e68c198","tid":40792,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T18:14:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好大怨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />